attributes.description: Dashboard providing statistics about URL type indicators from the abuse.ch integration

params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard is an overview of the different threat intelligence indicators with a **threat.indicator.type: url**.  

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of your indicators like popular domains, file extensions, statistics about how many unique indicators are ingested and other relevant information.

**[Integrations Page](/app/integrations/detail/ti_abusech/overview)**
